ğŸ“˜ Project Overview

This project focuses on creating a simple Water Level Monitoring System using an ultrasonic sensor and Arduino. The system helps monitor the water level in an overhead tank and provides visual and audio alerts using LEDs and a buzzer.

This solution helps prevent unnoticed low water levels and allows maintenance staff or students to take timely action.

ğŸ’¡ Features

Real-time water level measurement using an ultrasonic sensor.

LED indicator alerts for medium and low water levels.

Buzzer alert when water level is critically low.

Simple and low-cost prototype suitable for school demonstration.

