âš™ï¸ How the System Works

The ultrasonic sensor sends sound waves and measures the distance to the water surface.

Based on distance readings:

10â€“15 cm â†’ Level 1 LED turns ON
(Indicates medium water level)

<10 cm â†’ Level 2 LED + Buzzer activate
(Indicates critical almost full level)

>15 cm or safe zone â†’ All alerts remain OFF
